sub_title: Managing Partner | Mach49 | Quantum Delta | Kickstart AI | AR | Vision Pro | Venture Building | Co-founder Techleap.NL
summary:
Since building my first company I've been fascinated by building ventures that scale. Transforming tech ideas into business is what I live for. Lucky enough to have been part of some of most powerful teams out there. Skilled in building strong partnerships leveraging product, and business development resources. Passionate about consumer tech and services. Fascinated by interplanetary travel, and all things sci-fi.

Let’s dive into some of the reasons why you should definitely reach out to me.

You’re J.J. Abrams coming back to me on my Star Wars Cameo (took you long enough ;).
You want to build a (corporate) venture that actually scales.
You have a market entry challenge.
You want to define your Why, How and What to make doing stuff easier.
You want to find the best product/market/investor fit.

Feel free to reach out to me via whatsapp +31(0)6-31633669.
